Environmental Law









Academics & Faculty





Where Education Meets Innovation
Our academic approach is both demanding and rewarding, spurring students to strive for success and maximize their potential. But they never do it alone: world-class faculty guide our students, creating a supportive atmosphere and encouraging them to push beyond what seems possible. Renowned researchers, educators, and mentors, our faculty specialize in areas ranging from business and corporate law to public policy and criminal and civil litigation.
Our broad-based curriculum combines traditional classroom methods with expansive experiential learning options. Clinics, externships, advocacy programs, simulations, and other practical opportunities prepare students to practice from day one. 







Play





 Meet Dean Rougeau
"You are going to be challenged. You are going to be learning from people who are constantly challenging themselves." 











 











