Our Academic Philosophy
We prepare students for professional success at the highest level—and in a way uniquely suited to each person's particular talents. Professor and Associate Dean of Faculty Alfred Chueh-Chin Yen explains what sets our faculty apart, and why our collaborative approach works so well.
